PROJECT: Studio Mouton Noir Tattoo Website

Build a modern, high-end website for a tattoo studio called:

Studio Mouton Noir

Location:
Châteauguay, Quebec, Canada

Contact email:
studio.moutonoir@gmail.com

Instagram:
https://www.instagram.com/studiomoutonoir/

------------------------------------------------

BRAND PHILOSOPHY

“L'art de ne pas faire comme les autres.”

The black sheep is the one who stands apart, who embraces who they are and transforms their difference into strength.

Studio Mouton Noir is a creative tattoo studio where every tattoo is designed to express individuality.

The studio is not about mass production or generic flash tattoos.

Each piece is intentional, personal, and artistic.

The website should communicate:

individuality  
creativity  
rebellion  
artistry  
identity

Tone should feel artistic, modern, and slightly rebellious — like a tattoo studio combined with a contemporary art gallery.

Visitors should feel like they are entering a creative space, not just a service business.

------------------------------------------------

DESIGN DIRECTION

The design should be dark, minimal, editorial and premium.

Visual inspiration:

modern tattoo studios  
fashion brand websites  
underground art studios

Color palette:

#0A0A0A (black)
#161616 (charcoal)
#F3F3F3 (off white)
muted red accent

Typography:

Headlines:
bold condensed font
strong visual presence

Body:
modern sans serif
clean and readable

Design characteristics:

large imagery
lots of negative space
smooth scrolling
subtle animations
hover effects for portfolio items

The website should feel high-end and artistic.

------------------------------------------------

WEBSITE STRUCTURE

1. HERO SECTION

Full screen hero.

Background:
video or large image of tattooing process.

Headline:

L'art de ne pas faire comme les autres.

Subheadline:

Le mouton noir, c’est celui qui se démarque.
Celui qui assume qui il est.

Au Studio Mouton Noir, chaque tatouage est une façon d’exprimer ton identité.

Primary buttons:

Voir les artistes
Prendre rendez-vous

------------------------------------------------

2. ABOUT / PHILOSOPHY

Title:

Pourquoi “Mouton Noir”?

Text:

Le mouton noir, c’est celui qui ne suit pas le troupeau — celui qui se démarque, qui assume qui il est, qui transforme sa différence en force.

Au Studio Mouton Noir, chaque tatouage est une façon d’exprimer ton individualité.

On ne fait pas simplement de l’encre sur la peau.

On raconte ton histoire.

C’est un espace créatif, sans jugement, où chaque design est pensé avec intention et personnalité.

Ici, tu n’es pas un client parmi d’autres.

Tu es l’œuvre.

------------------------------------------------

3. ARTISTS

Display a grid of tattoo artists.

Each artist card should include:

photo
name
tattoo style
Instagram link
button to view portfolio

Artist pages should include:

bio
style description
tattoo gallery
booking button

------------------------------------------------

4. PORTFOLIO

Create a gallery of tattoos.

Grid layout with hover effects.

When hovering:

show artist name
tattoo style

Images should be large and high quality.

------------------------------------------------

5. TATTOO PROCESS

Explain the tattoo journey.

Section with 4 steps.

Consultation  
We discuss your idea and inspiration.

Design  
We create a custom design that fits your vision.

Tattoo Session  
Your tattoo is created in a professional and safe environment.

Aftercare  
We guide you through the healing process.

------------------------------------------------

6. BOOKING / CONSULTATION

Create a booking form.

Fields:

Name
Email
Tattoo idea
Placement on body
Size
Budget
Reference images upload

Submit button:

Réserver une consultation

Form submissions should send an email to:

studio.moutonoir@gmail.com

------------------------------------------------

7. INSTAGRAM SECTION

Embed or dynamically pull posts from:

https://www.instagram.com/studiomoutonoir/

Display latest tattoo posts in a grid.

------------------------------------------------

8. LOCATION

Map section.

Show:

Studio Mouton Noir
Châteauguay, Québec

Include contact email:

studio.moutonoir@gmail.com

