TECHNICAL REQUIREMENTS

Site must be:

mobile first
fast loading
SEO friendly
clean modern layout

Animations should be subtle and smooth.

Use modern responsive design.

Images should scale properly on mobile.

The site should feel premium and artistic.

------------------------------------------------

GOAL OF THE WEBSITE

The main goal is to:

1. showcase tattoo artistry
2. express the brand philosophy
3. drive consultation bookings

Visitors should feel inspired to book a tattoo consultation.

The site should feel like entering a creative tattoo studio rather than a traditional business website.
One small but powerful thing you should add later
Tell Claude to also create:
a “Flash Tattoos” page